data.config.yaml:
tunnel: 6ff4dfd7-2b77-4a4f-84d9-3241bea658dc
credentials-file: /etc/cloudflared/token/token
protocol: quic
no-autoupdate: true
metrics: 0.0.0.0:2000

# Enable WARP routing for private network connectivity
warp-routing:
  enabled: true

# Ingress rules for node-specific services
ingress:
  # Kubernetes API proxy for cross-node communication
  - hostname: "*.nodes.k3s.boathou.se"
    service: https://kubernetes.default.svc.cluster.local:443
    originRequest:
      noTLSVerify: false
      caPool: /var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/ca.crt

  # GPU metrics endpoint for Calypso
  - hostname: gpu.k3s.boathou.se
    service: http://localhost:9400
    originRequest:
      noTLSVerify: true

  # Pod-to-pod communication via tunnel (for cross-NAT networking)
  - hostname: "*.pod.k3s.boathou.se"
    service: tcp://localhost:10250
    originRequest:
      noTLSVerify: true

  # Default catch-all
  - service: http_status:404
